translated: Margaret Thatcher, born 13 October 1925 in Grantham and died April 8, 2013 in London, was UK Prime Minister between 1979 and 1990.
original: Margaret Thatcher, née le 13 octobre 1925 à Grantham et morte le 8 avril 2013 à Londres, a été Premier ministre du Royaume-Uni entre 1979 et 1990.
